---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
import Comments from '../../../components/Comments.astro';
---

<Layout title="Blockquotes - Markdown Tutorial" description="Learn how to create blockquotes in Markdown." lang="en">
  <Header />

  <main>
    <section class="section section-dark">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <p class="text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase text-[var(--color-terracotta)] mb-4">
            Basic Syntax / Blockquotes
          </p>
          <h1 class="font-serif-display text-[var(--text-inverse)] mb-6">Blockquotes</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-[var(--text-on-dark)] opacity-80" style="line-height: 1.6;">
            Use blockquotes to present content from other sources.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container max-w-4xl">
        <div class="prose">
          <h2>Basic Syntax</h2>
          <p>To create a blockquote, add a > symbol in front of a paragraph:</p>
          <pre><code>{`> Dorothy followed her through many of the beautiful rooms in her castle.`}</code></pre>

          <h2>Multiple Paragraphs</h2>
          <p>Blockquotes can contain multiple paragraphs. Add a > on the blank line between paragraphs:</p>
          <pre><code>{`> Dorothy followed her through many of the beautiful rooms in her castle.
>
> The Witch bade her clean the pots and kettles and sweep the floor.`}</code></pre>

          <h2>Nested Blockquotes</h2>
          <p>Blockquotes can be nested. Add a >> symbol for nested paragraphs:</p>
          <pre><code>{`> Dorothy followed her through many of the beautiful rooms in her castle.
>
>> The Witch bade her clean the pots and kettles.`}</code></pre>

          <h2>Blockquotes with Other Elements</h2>
          <p>Blockquotes can contain other Markdown formatting elements:</p>
          <pre><code>{`> #### The quarterly results look great!
>
> - Revenue was off the chart.
> - Profits were higher than ever.
>
> *Everything* is going according to **plan**.`}</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <Comments slug="basic-blockquotes" />
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
